# AI Video Generation: "The Eddie AI Revolution"

The goal is to use the cloned Remotion project to generate a high-retention YouTube Short focused on the "Eddie AI" editor (using the provided transcript). This will demonstrate the full power of the "Agentic" workflow by combining news curation, visual mastermind aesthetics, and Remotion orchestration.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **API Credentials Needed**: To generate the voiceover and structured script, I need you to provide the following API keys in the `.env` file (or I can help you set them up):
> - `OPENAI_API_KEY`: For script generation.
> - `ELEVENLABS_API_KEY`: For high-quality voiceover.
> - `TAVILY_API_KEY` (Optional): If you want me to fetch live news sentiment from Reddit/Web.

> [!WARNING]
> **Missing Source Video**: The project refers to an MP4 (`Best AI Video Editor... .mp4`) that is not in the repository. I will fallback to high-quality **AI-Generated images** using the `generate_image` tool to ensure the video can still be rendered.

## Proposed Changes

### 1. Configuration & Orchestration
- **[NEW] `.env`**: Create a `.env` file from the example once keys are provided.
- **[MODIFY] [Root.tsx](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/remotionVideos/src/Root.tsx)**: Register a new composition `eddie-ai-short` specifically for this generation.

### 2. Asset Generation
- **[NEW] Scripts/Images**: I will use the `generate_image` tool to create a series of 8-10 high-end "Cyberpunk Editor" and "AI Interface" visuals to replace the missing MP4.
- **[NEW] Voiceover**: Use the existing `remotion-voiceover` skill to generate audio for each scene once ElevenLabs is configured.

### 3. Component Implementation
- **[MODIFY] [NewsShortV2.tsx](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/remotionVideos/src/components/NewsShortV2.tsx)**: I will adapt this component (or create a variant) to use the new "Eddie AI" script. This component is chosen because it supports **true word-syncing** and broadcast-level aesthetics.

